---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about Ivan Trajanovski, a mobile developer based in Austria"
	pubDate={new Date("January 20 2025")}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>Hello! I'm Ivan Trajanovski, a mobile developer based in Autria.</p>

	<h2>Professional Journey</h2>
	<p>
		Throughout my career, I've had the opportunity to work with various mobile
		technologies and frameworks. My expertise spans across iOS and Android
		development, with proficiency in languages and frameworks like Swift,
		Kotlin, React Native, and Flutter.
	</p>

	<h2>Technical Skills</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>iOS Development: Swift, SwiftUI, UIKit</li>
		<li>Android Development: Kotlin, Jetpack Compose</li>
		<li>Cross-platform: React Native, Flutter</li>
		<li>Version Control: Git</li>
		<li>CI/CD: Jenkins, Fastlane</li>
		<li>Testing: XCTest, JUnit, Jest</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Beyond Coding</h2>
	<p>
		When I'm not immersed in code, I enjoy exploring Austria's stunning
		landscapes and keeping up with the latest trends in mobile development. I'm
		always eager to learn new technologies and contribute to the mobile
		development community.
	</p>

	<h2>Let's Connect</h2>
	<p>
		I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers and potential
		collaborators. Whether you want to discuss mobile development, potential
		projects, or just want to say hi, feel free to reach out!
	</p>
</Layout>
